    "shortName": {
      "zh": "6B5-16",
      "en": "6B5-16"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "6B5“蜂箱”防弹胸挂于 1986 年正式获苏联军队装备。其中 6B5-16 型采用钛质防弹板，面对炮弹破片以及轻武器子弹打击可提供三级防护，还设置有几个弹匣包与杂物收纳包。",
      "en": "The 6B5 bulletproof vest was adopted by the armed forces of the USSR in 1986. Option 6B5-16 is designed to protect against fragments and bullets of fire arms (class 3 protection, titanium). Also has several pouches for magazines and other equipment."
    },
